{
  "stem": "6803.2",
  "chunk_idx": 12,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I was no more than 60 pounds, or maybe-- maybe 50, 50, 60 pounds, but my will was just to be liberated, to be able to be free, to be counted like a man.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "That's what I wanted.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And will is more than power sometimes, you know?",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And, uh, I remember one evening-- the first day, Saturday.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I was looking in a window there, and there is a truck stopped in the street.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And there is a colored soldier came over, and he says, sleep, sleep, sleep?",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I didn't know what he meant, so the people from the truck-- also my kind of people-- come on, [SPEAKING GERMAN].",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "They're going to take us to put us to sleep, somewhere to go to sleep.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "To rest.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So went on the truck, and they took us to Linz, to Linz.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And we stayed there in-- overnight.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And then in the morning, I says, I'm not going to stay here.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I'm going to go back to Wels.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And soon as I walk out from there in the morning, I met-- I found a friend of mine.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "We were growing up together in the same hometown.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "His name was Alter.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "He still lives in-- in New York now.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "His name is Alter Pollack.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And so we stood together like-- like two brothers, and we walked back from Guns-- from Linz into Wels.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And then I realized how much American--",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah, for three or four days.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Three or four days we walked.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Don't know how many miles.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We walked about three days, yeah.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So we walked, and every time we walked in a little-- in a house, and we ask-- ask them for food.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And they gave us food.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I mean-- it was no-- we walked back to, uh-- we walked back to Wels.",
      "word_count": 15
    }
  ],
